You MUST enter a username and date of birth to continue.\
The username cannot be a duplicate of any other username in the database, and cannon be an empty string.\
The date of birth too cannot be empty and must be entered in the format of (MM/DD/YYYY).\
Failure to comply with result in an error message.\
\
