Here you must enter the username and date of birth to log into the game.\
\
Once logged in the game will be presented.\
If it is your birthday today then the title will display happy birthday. \
Due to you being a new user the stats are all set to 0.\
You may select any Rock, Paper, Scissors, Lizard or Spock button to start the game.\
After you select a button, the corresponding result win be displayed and the your stats will be incremented as such.\
You are now forced to chose from two buttons, whether you want to play again or log out.\
\
The Play again button will repeat the process again.\
\
The log out button will lead you back to the home screen where you are unable to play and must register or log in.\
\
If you Log in with the same user you are able to carry on your statistics from the previous games\
